✅ Features in This Version
Calibration at start → automatically finds center & max torque.
Smooth ramping → soft acceleration/deceleration like a PID without feedback.
Keyboard control → Left/Right arrows steer.
Emergency stop → ESC instantly sets torque to 0.
Torque scaling live adjustment → + / - keys adjust strength on-the-fly.
No oscillation → ramping prevents jerks or jumps.
Driver can overpower wheel → torque only assists, doesn’t fight the driver.
